<p><strong>Data sources:</strong> Filing, disposition, and chapter-mix data from the <a href="https://www.fjc.gov/research/idb" rel="external">Federal Judicial Center Integrated Database</a>. Docket coverage from the <a href="https://free.law/" rel="external">Free Law Project</a>'s <a href="https://www.courtlistener.com/recap/" rel="external">RECAP Archive</a>. Privacy-rule context from the Federal Judicial Center's April 2024 study on unredacted SSNs in PACER. Content derived on this index is published under <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/" rel="external">CC BY-SA 4.0</a>.</p>
<p style="margin-top:12px"><strong>Scope note:</strong> This index covers US federal bankruptcy cases recorded in the Federal Judicial Center's Integrated Database. The Open Bankruptcy Project does not reproduce docket PDFs or filing text on this domain - all primary-source access is via CourtListener. Last updated 2026-04-21.</p>
